observations.recommendation:
We recommended and Management agreed to:

Maintain all efforts to maximize the utilization of the fund and ensure the achievement of the optimum implementation of projects that will ultimately promote and contribute to the inclusive economic growth and development of the LGU;

Expedite the completion of the nine (9) projects while maintaining quality workmanship in order for the constituents to finally enjoy the services these projects would render;

Strategize scheme to ensure that the identified projects/programs are implementation ready, otherwise facilitate the realignment thereof; and

Direct the Municipal Engineer and the MENRO to properly supervise and monitor the deployment of manpower when simultaneous project undertakings occur.

observations.managementAction:
The LCE directed the concerned office heads through memorandum order to:

a) Maintain all efforts to maximize the utilization of the fund and ensure the achievement of the optimum implementation of projects that will ultimately promote and contribute to the inclusive economic growth and development of the LGU;

b) Expedite the completion of the nine (9) projects while maintaining quality workmanship in order for the constituents to finally enjoy the services these projects would render;

c) Strategize scheme to ensure that the identified projects/programs are implementation ready, otherwise facilitate the realignment thereof; and

d)  Direct the Municipal Engineer and the MENRO to properly supervise and monitor the deployment of manpower when simultaneous project undertakings occur.

